subSubSection.paragraph:
Female sexual characters : vulva large, covering 2/3 of coxa, extending mesally to half of prefemur (
Fig. 2I
). Operculum rounded, very slightly invaginated medially, mesal margin strongly projecting into a well-rounded lobe twice as high as remaining operculum. Subanal plate : large, shaped like a wide, well-rounded triangle, in some females with a slight invagination at the highest point of apical margin, creating two wide, well-rounded lobes.

